{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"285","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"海水溫度若再上升 科學家：北極熊將於本世紀滅絕","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/0525.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 553px;' /><span style='color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 新細明體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(234, 234, 234);'>科學家指出，若海水溫度持續上升，北極熊恐於2100年滅絕。（歐新社）</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 新細明體, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);'>科學家日前研究指出，若海水溫度持續上升，多數海洋生物將會消失，並使海洋食物鏈發生劇烈改變，而北極熊也將在2100年滅絕。</p>\n\n<ul class='pic300 boxTitle' data-desc='小圖' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 新細明體, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; width: 314px; float: left; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);'>\n</ul>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 新細明體, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);'>綜合外媒報導，北卡羅來納那大學（North Carolina State University）和佛羅里達理工學院（Florida Institute of Technology）共同研究表示，若海水溫度以攝氏2.8度升幅持續上升，西元2100年恐導致眾多海洋生物無法承受而滅絕。</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 新細明體, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);'>科學家阿洛森（Richard Aronson）更指出，暖化將威脅極地生態系統，包含北極熊和企鵝等指標性動物。</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 新細明體, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);'>研究人員說明，海洋保護區已失去保護作用，難以抵擋全球暖化造成的衝擊，佛羅里達群島國家的海洋保護區內，已有大量珊瑚因高溫引起白化與疾病。此外，暖化導致海水氧濃度下降，將不再適合多數物種棲息。</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 新細明體, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);'>全球目前有8236個海洋保護區，卻不到海洋總面積的4%，若溫室氣體持續排放導致海水溫度上升，現有的保護措施恐在2100年失效。</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 新細明體, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);'>阿洛森表示，溫室氣體捕捉的熱，有9成都是被海水給吸收，南北極的野生動物將最先受到威脅。</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 新細明體, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 新細明體, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 30px; font-family: Arial, helvetica, 微軟正黑體, Geneva, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 新細明體, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);'>資料來源:http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2422837</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2018-05-25","clk_count":"101"}},"__N_SSG":true}